STATEMENT: >>>
When working_memory.enabled is false, working-memory lookup shall return an empty list.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-WORKING-CURRENT-FILE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Working Memory History Scope
STATEMENT: >>>
Working-memory lookup shall be restricted to the active file_id.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-WORKING-LATEST
STATUS: Draft
