RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-GOLD-ENABLE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Gold Lookup Enable Dependency
STATEMENT: >>>
When episodic_memory.enabled is false, current Gold lookup shall return an empty list.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-GOLD-CURRENT-FILE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Gold History Scope
STATEMENT: >>>
Gold lookup shall be restricted to the active file_id.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-GOLD-LATEST
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Gold Ordering and Limit
STATEMENT: >>>
Gold lookup shall select latest Gold records ordered by created_at_utc descending and limited by max_gold_records; the current baseline is 1.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-ENABLE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Direct Recall Enable Switch
STATEMENT: >>>
When direct_recall.enabled is false or the key is empty, Direct Recall lookup shall return no candidate.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-EXACT
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Exact Direct Recall Match
STATEMENT: >>>
Direct Recall shall match direct_recall_key by exact SQLite equality rather than semantic similarity.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-ROOT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-CROSS-FILE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Direct Recall Cross-History Scope
STATEMENT: >>>
Direct Recall may search all indexed memory histories and is the current explicit cross-history retrieval path.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-EXACT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-EXCLUDE
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Direct Recall Tag Exclusion
STATEMENT: >>>
Direct Recall shall exclude configured tags; the current baseline excludes Black.
<<<
RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-EXACT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-PRIORITY
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Direct Recall Result Priority
STATEMENT: >>>
When multiple exact matches exist, current ordering shall prefer Gold, then Green, then other tags, and then latest created_at_utc.
