- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-DIRECT-EXACT

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-LOOKUP-FILE-ROW
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: File Metadata Attachment
STATEMENT: >>>
Deterministic candidates shall attach the corresponding memory_files row and paired history title and filenames.
