RELATIONS:
- TYPE: Parent
  VALUE: GHOST-MEM-IR-LOOKUP-BODY

[REQUIREMENT]
UID: GHOST-MEM-IR-LOOKUP-JSON-LIST
STATUS: Draft
TITLE: Indexed JSON List Parsing
STATEMENT: >>>
Keyword and file-snapshot SQLite JSON fields shall parse to lists when valid and shall become empty lists when invalid.
